## Best Practices

### DO ✅

```ruby
# Test response codes
assert_response :success
assert_response :redirect
assert_response :unprocessable_entity

# Test database changes
assert_difference('Article.count', 1)

# Test redirects
assert_redirected_to article_url(@article)

# Test flash messages
assert_equal "Success!", flash[:notice]

# Test authentication
sign_in_as @user
get protected_url
assert_response :success

# Test authorization
sign_in_as other_user
get edit_article_url(@article)
assert_redirected_to root_url
```

### DON'T ❌

```ruby
# Don't test view rendering details in controller tests
# Use system tests for that

# Don't test business logic in controllers
# That belongs in model tests

# Don't make unnecessary database calls
# Use fixtures efficiently
```

